channel.title: [317]ZurielPKs - [Delta Based]
channel.description:
[center][COLOR=blue].-._.You don't even know its Deltascape.-._.[/COLOR][/CENTER]
Source Download --- http://www.mediafire.com/?tm0hnacmnmm --- 5.07MB Client Download --- http://www.mediafire.com/?55jujdjqjhm --- 56.8 MB
Features
[ul][*]Economy Is Shit.. needs to be worked on... several items are highly overpowered, most skills generate massive amounts of gold, monsters drop shit tons of items/cash [*]Item duping has been fixed in the following ways: Trade dupe, Offer X dupe, Telegrab dupe, and xlog dupe.GF Delta [*]Fully animated and working Gods, God Bosses, God Creatures, Bosses, and Most NPCs. [*]Removed and fixed dead code fragments, cleaned the source, streamlined the programming code. Increased stability and performance. This is truly a reliable source.[/ul]
Weapons
[ul][*]Every poisoned weapon has the proper poisoning effect (p)-(+)-(s) [*]Regan ring gives you +1 hp every 10 seconds [*]Dragon weapons all have special attacks with proper animations, effects, and graphics [*]Barrows armor like Dharok's and Guthan's have the proper effects [*]Dragon claw four hitting special attack with the real Runescape animation [*]Bronze, Iron, Steel, Mithril, Adamant, and runite crossbows [*]Bronze, Iron, Silver, Blurite, steel, mithril, adamant, runite, jade, sapphire, emerald, ruby, diamond, and dragonstone crossbow bolts [*]Instant dragon dagger special attack [*] Bronze, iron, steel, mithril, adamant, and runite knives work just like runescape[/ul]
Player Vs Environment
[ul][*]Fixed no clipping for npcs and players in major areas [*]Recreated the combat formula to bring you the best out of the PvE gaming experience[/ul]
Mini games
[ul][*]Battalion - Like assault but in a different place with better npcs, better rewards, and better game play [*]Fightpits - Completely revamped from the Deltascape version, now with a reward npc [*]Fightcaves - A fantastic 64 wave battle for your life [*]Barrows - Dig up some graves and fight some ghost before battling your way to the chest to claim your reward [*]Godwars - After killing 20 of the most deadliest monsters in the game head to one of the four godwars caverns to battle one of the four fully animated bosses and their minions[/ul]
Skilling
[ul][*]Most skills have been completed, and are functional. Highly recommended to set the XP Rates.[/ul]

List of Commands
ADMIN COMMANDS [ul][*]xteleto [*]xteletome [*]alltome [*]admin (playername) --gives admin status [*]mod (playername) --gives mod status [*]delect (playername) --makes regular player [*]add (playername) --gives premium status [*]remove (playername) --removes premium status [*]give (number) (playername) --gives a specific number of DONATOR POINTS to a player [*]take (number) (playername)--removes a specific number of DONATOR POINTS from a player [*]mute (playername) [*]ban (playername) [*]ipban (playername) [*]alert --send a NOTICE from the server [*]update (seconds) --adds a countdown, before saving all players, and mass kicking [*]smite (playername) --instantly kills a player [*]healall --heals all players in combat [*]restore (playername) --restores the player's heath (must be in combat)[/ul]
Moderator Commands [ul][*]kick (playername) [*]jail (playername) [*]tele [*]xteleto[/ul]
User Commands [ul][*]rules [*]updates [*]news [*]commands [*]battilion [*]pkpoints [*]mypoints [*]party -- sends player to the party room[/ul]
Please note the username in the animated graphics.
This is a[B] completely legit source[/B]. There is no need for me to perform a virus scan, as a virus scan [B]WILL NOT PICK UP MALICIOUS BYTECODE[/B]. [B]If you don't know me/trust me by now, [I]then don't download[/I][/B]. Honestly. Last thing I need is a bunch of 12 year olds, wetting their pants, wondering if the [B]Dread Pirate Luvodicus[/B] is sending backdoor trojans into their Mommy's computer...
I am fully aware that the Development Team currently working on ZurielPKs does NOT wish me to release this, however, I have placed MORE time and energy in developing this source, have done MORE WORK server sided, have been hosting and using this source since OCT '09. [B][I][U]This source is what I GAVE to the team, in which they deleted their work, and continued from where I left off. I am the ORIGINAL DEVELOPER of this source.[/U][/I][/B] It was always a wish of mine to release a completed source for Various Programmers, and Newbs, as I am a firm believer of Open Source, Software Piracy, and Peer to Peer Sharing... If anyone wishes to speak, in private, my other reasons, as well as various conversation snippets, screen caps, and other novelties, please contact me, and keep it out of this thread.
Anyone who screams LEECH: [B][U]GTFO, and develop something Original.[/U][/B] Out of the THOUSANDS of users in the RSPS community, and the TENS of users who scream leech.. maybe ONE of you have released and compiled a completely original source, never downloaded, never given. As well as the fact [B][I]I'M ACTUALLY RELEASING A SOURCE[/I][/B]... Let's see [B]Owner-Josh[/B], or the [B][I]fagots at CrisisX[/I][/B], do the same...
